title: Canada 's biodiesel production 2007 to 2019
summary: Overall Production in million liters has increased over the Year.
Production in million liters is roughly constant from 2007 to 2012, gradually increasing from 2012 to 2014, and finally roughly constant from 2014 to 2015.
The line rapidly increased by 120.75% from Year 2013 to 2014.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2013 and 2014.
The highest Production in million liters, of value 351.0 was reached at Year 2014
Minimum Production in million liters about 70.0 was reached at Year 2007
